<li><a href="#orgdbe9979">12. Biochemical tests for the identification of bacteria. Tests for determination of carbolytic, proteolytic enzymes and oxidoreductases. Other tests.</a></li>
<li><a href="#org4d4960d">13. Kligler’s polytrope medium (Triple Sugar Iron Agar): composition, inoculation and reading.</a></li>
<li><a href="#org95b4c8d">14. Quantitative methods for the determination of bacterial growth: enumeration with optical standard and determination of microbial count on a solid medium</a></li>
