<div id="outline-container-orgd7ab645" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgd7ab645">Characteristics</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgd7ab645">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>All streptococci are catalase negative(-)</li>
<li>Susceptible to penicillin</li>
<li>Commonly arranged in chains</li>
