<div id="outline-container-org5e2db10" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org5e2db10">37.Neisseria - N. Gonorrhea</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-org5e2db10">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Gram negative, intracellular, aerobic diplococci</li>
<li>Sexual transmission</li>
<li>NO polysaccharide capsule</li>
<li>NO maltose fermentation</li>
<li>NO vaccine due to antigenic variation of pilus proteins</li>
</ul>

<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


