<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Transmission:
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Inhalation of infected aerosols e.g infected air-conditioning system</li>
<li><i>Only Legionella species that hydrolyzes hippurate</i></li>
<li>More common in smokers</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
