</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left">ONLY humans</td>
<td class="org-left">Stained using Ziehl-Neelsen stain:</td>
<td class="org-left">Cord factor:</td>
<td class="org-left">Tuberculosis</td>
<td class="org-left"><b>RIPE</b></td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">-&gt;Binds to mycolic acid</td>
<td class="org-left">-&gt;Arranges M.Tuberculosis in serpentine factor</td>
<td class="org-left">-&gt;Affects lungs</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
