<td class="org-left">TNF-a release and activation of macrophages</td>
<td class="org-left">-&gt;Typically dormant</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">Facultative intracellular</td>
<td class="org-left">Surface glycolipids(sulfatides):</td>
<td class="org-left">-&gt;Reactivation by immunosuppresion</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
